 a^2 > b^2 \iff a > b \vee a < -b
 a^2 < b^2 \iff -|b| < a < |b|
 |a| < b \iff -b < a < b
P((X-EX)^2 > a^2) \leq \frac{EY}{a^2} \iff P(-|X-EX| < a < |X-EX|) \leq \frac{EY}{a^2} 
